# Library 
pip install Faker
pip install pylint
pip install flake8

# Project structure
```bash
reservations
|__database
|____table.txt
|__test
|____test.py
|_class.py
```
# Unit tests

## Run unit tests while at the root:

```bash
python -m reservations.test.hotel_test
python -m reservations.test.customer_test
python -m reservations.test.reservation_test
```

# Lint

## Run pylint while at the root:

```bash
pylint reservations.hotel
pylint reservations.test.hotel_test
pylint reservations.customer
pylint reservations.test.customer_test
pylint reservations.hotels
pylint reservations.test.hotels_test
```

# Flake8 

## Run pylint while at the root:

```bash
flake8 .\reservations\hotel.py
flake8 .\reservations\test\hotel_test.py
flake8 .\reservations\customer.py
flake8 .\reservations\test\customer_test.py
flake8 .\reservations\hotels.py
flake8 .\reservations\test\hotels_test.py
```
